The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods, specifically LSTMs, for time series prediction. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), indicating that these sub-categories are also relevant. Finally, the paper discusses the use of evolutionary computation, which falls under the category of swarm intelligence (cs.SI).
